description:
Scripts for the netsquid simulations that produces figures 2a and 2b in the paper&nbsp;&quot;A benchmarking procedure for quantum networks&quot;, together with pickled outputs of these simulations that produce the plots. 

 &nbsp; 

 Note that the plotting scripts&nbsp;(2_chain_plot.py, n_chain_plot.py)&nbsp;require pickled data to work. These pickles&nbsp;can be obtained by running the associated protocol scripts&nbsp;( 2_chain.py, n_chain.py) or by downloading the associated data supplement (data.zip). 

 Running&nbsp;the Netsquid code requires Netsquid version 0.7 (and will not work with newer versions).&nbsp;Netsquid can be downloaded  here &nbsp;. 

 &nbsp; 

 &nbsp;

